                "name": "天火"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 53,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   忽然產生了靈感，忘記換衣服直接衝出家門，等遇到了麻煩才發現穿著問題。",
                "name": "天火"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 54,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   我不記得因為這樣的事情燒毀過多少裙子了。",
                "name": "天火"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 55,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_145_prove_1",
                "name2": "char_166_skfire_3#3",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 56,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   唔，我覺得這似乎不是應該用理所當然的口吻來描述的事？",
                "name": "普羅旺斯"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 57,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_348_ceylon_4#2"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 58,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   姑且不論裙子的事情，大致上你的判斷沒有錯。",
                "name": "錫蘭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 59,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_145_prove_1"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 60,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   該說什麼好呢，這麼做還是有些危險的哦......沒有準備完全的話。",
                "name": "普羅旺斯"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 61,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_145_prove_1",
                "name2": "char_166_skfire_3#3",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 62,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   沒事。只要我在，哪怕是兩手空空出門也會很安全。",
                "name": "天火"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 63,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_348_ceylon_4#5",
                "name2": "char_145_prove_1",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 64,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   總之，謝謝你們救了我。",
                "name": "錫蘭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 65,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   等回到市內時，可以來找我，我會報答你們。",
